Mode

Description

`Truncate`

Towards zero (default C# behavior)

`Floor`

Towards negative infinity

`Ceiling`

Towards positive infinity

`AwayFromZero`

Away from zero

`Euclidean`

floor(x / abs(n)) \* sign(n)

